WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy B2-M01: Identity, goals and learner profile. Learners practise argue a point through introductions, routines, aspirations, personal information. The teacher models perfect and continuous aspect review, introduces vocabulary such as personal details, goals, classroom objects, numbers, dates, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
